snippet.title: My Douchey Boss Has a Gentle Twin Brother?! - Boys Love (BL) Visual Novel
snippet.description:
Kyle's new boss, Vincent, is mischievous and eccentric. One day, Kyle bumps into his boss after work and is surprised when his superior acts kind. Later, he finds out he'd actually met his boss' twin brother, Vernon. The brothers are estranged, but what happens when they fall for the same person?

Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2582240/My_Douchey_Boss_Has_a_Gentle_Twin_Brother__BL_Visual_Novel/
